islike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T01:21:52.000Z","msg":"侵侵應該即時禁止出口往支那，咁俄羅斯就變獨市，即時加價，侵侵再用高價恢復供應俾支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed41d5ebbe8ef46da9e5a0f5120122e2cf2a3588","tid":876781,"uid":131157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T01:22:20.000Z","msg":"借關稅搜刮國內民脂民膏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb5b6c409590598d15451bdb3901c92f0161d2bc","tid":876781,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T01:31:48.000Z","msg":"發達啦,又可以收鳩佢老母關稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f8763fa759d064124f029596a23fb8c32299b8","tid":876781,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T01:39:53.000Z","msg":"成個報復戇鳩之中戇鳩邊有人用自己短處去打人長處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"376776e9ac78a397775b4a2254b21a602197134c","tid":876781,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T01:40:46.000Z","msg":"以為佢同俄羅斯買"},{"pid":"2bd40d7bbaf2a5bbb4ba67f303035038bbbf7977","tid":876781,"uid":108347,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T01:50:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P6H5TxF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP6H5TxF.png&h=d390ef6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dffa9b046064da62e0f6388321b15c8ad288008d","tid":876781,"uid":203681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T01:56:08.000Z","msg":"支那又然"},{"pid":"a68a2d8ce6d9152604065116f00bdc3f153a3d17","tid":876781,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T0